captions.text:
We'll play “Improbable School”.
Andy will be our teacher.

He'll go to that corner, he won't
listen to what we're making up.

The teacher must guess
who are his students.

Our producers made up
characters for these students.

We have here... Dani will
do a ‘coward carbon atom’.

Renata will do a
‘Barbie supermarket cashier’.

And Elidio, you will
create his character.

Babysitter?
I like that.
Babysitting what?

The Hulk?
Cool, ‘Hulk's babysitter’!

So let's begin
“Improbable School”!

Recess is over,
come on, teacher!

Let's do the roll call.
Number 1!

You say I'm a coward, I'm not fond!
I'm doing my covalent bonds!
I clapped my hands a lot for you.

Wassup, guys?
Cool? Cool? Cool?

Wassup, guys?
Cool? Cool? Cool?
Yeah, dawg!

Which letter differentiate
male and female chromosomes?

- Male from female?
- Yes.

Can I make a call
so I can guess?

I'm bonding with
a lot people, you know?

- Yes.
- Hello? Wassup, Oxygen?
Yeah, dawg!

Nah, that guy don't mix with anyone,
he's like a noble gas or something.

I just stayed at home. We went
to Nitrogen, that was so cool!

Yo, the teach is asking me
about male and female stuff,

I don't have a gender, so I'm
not into it... Do you know it?

Ya been in a lot of
lungs, give me a hint...

You don't know?
You're getting high, all right.

Say hi to Gold! That bastard!
See ya, goodbye!
Yeah, teacher, I don't know.
It was just a ring...

- Fine, you got an ‘F’.
- Got! An ‘F’..
Got! An ‘F’…

- Number 2!
- Helooo! Here...

So, what's the question...
Sorry, I swallowed the system!
Holy shit, it's in the system...

- Number 2...
- Go ahead!

- Yes, thank you.
- May I say something?

- Yes.
- More people go with Visa!

- What is the capital of the state of Alagoas?
- Do you want this soda? There's a discount!

- Do you? Not really?
- No.

Would you like your
receipt in the bag?
I can't type. Okay!
You don't know the capital of Alagoas?
It's a swimming pool, of course!

- Okay, you got an ‘F’.
- Oh! Cool.
Number 3.

This boy leaves me so unsure!
I hope he soon gets mature!

Ask me, teacher!
I'll answer it!

I'll say it again:
What is the capital of Alagoas?

You know what,
I ended up there once!

- Really?
- I was working...

- What is your work?
- I can't say! You have to guess!

I was working...
Let's change this diaper...
He pooped a little...
I had a wet wipe for his tushie...

I got the wipe, but the boy kicked
me and I ended up in Alagoas!

- I'm worn out...
- But who is this boy?
You have to guess that too!
But he is not mature yet...
You got an ‘F’.

Lord, I won't be able to get
another job, I can't take it...

- Teacher, can you guess...
- I'll make a general question!

- Quick, time is running out...
- What is the capital of Alagoas?

I can ask my homie Aluminium,
his abbreviation is ‘Al’ too...

- Stay out of it, this question is just for us
- That's right...

- What color was the poop of...
- It was green...
It looked like he ate himself!

Looked like he
ate his own tongue!

- Who are the students, teacher?
- I'll give a shot.

Renata is a Barbie who's
a supermarket cashier.
Daniel is the carbon atom.

- Who gets scared easily.
- All right. Applause!

And Elidio is an old
lady babysitting the Hulk.

CIA. BARBIXAS DE HUMOR
presented

IMPROV¡VEL
Probably a good show.

- Really, boss?
- Actually, I'm pretending.

- What is the white fish?
- Nail-fish!
